        <div class="stock-outer">
         <!-- START OF CODE FOR QUOTEMEDIA CUSTOM COMPONENT DATA -->
         <script src="https://app.quotemedia.com/quotetools/jsVarsMultiQuotes.go?webmasterId=90338&amp;symbols=IT.TSXCII&amp;symbols=IV.JXI&amp;symbols=^DJI&amp;symbols=COMP&amp;symbols=^SP500&amp;symbols=$CADUSD&amp;symbols=/GCSPUSD&amp;symbols=/CL&amp;limit=200">
         </script>
         <script type="text/javascript">
          function qmcChg(i) {
        var change = qmQuotes[i].change;
        change = change.replace('<div class="qmjsleft">Change</div><div class="qmjsright">', '');
        change = change.replace('</div>', '');
        change = Number(change);
        if (i === 5) { change = change.toFixed(4); }
        else { change = change.toFixed(2); }
        if (change > 0) { qmcClass = "qmc_up"; qmcSign = "+"; }
        else if (change < 0) { qmcClass = "qmc_down"; qmcSign = ""; }
        else { qmcClass = ""; qmcSign = ""; }
        return "<span class='qmc_change_data " + qmcClass + "'>" + qmcSign + change + "</span>";
    }
    function qmcLast(i) {
        var last = qmQuotes[i].last;
        last = last.replace('<div class="qmjsleft">Last</div><div class="qmjsright">', '');
        last = last.replace('</div>', '');
        last = last.replace(',', '');
        last = Number(last);
        if (i === 5) { last = last.toFixed(4); }
        else { last = last.toFixed(2); }
        return '<div class="qmjsleft">Last</div><div class="qmjsright">' + last + '</div>';
    }

        nm = nm.replace('S&P/TSX  Comp', 'TSX');

        nm = nm.replace('USA', 'CAD/USD');
        nm = nm.replace('WTI Crude Oil', 'CRUDE');
        nm = nm.replace('Spot Gold US', 'GOLD');
        return nm;
    }
